The Fuzor gives a weak smile at Iron Raptor, and as soon as she moves her arms, the wing attatched to her back falls off. Her deep chest wound had stopped bleeding, and so had her punctured stomach and lungs, luckily. But her torn optic was still trickling as so was the slash on the back of her head. She felt woozy, probably from loss of mech-fluid.

She tries her best to speak in a clear voice "Yes, there are.. two more as far as I know. There's one called Ramhorn and another called Dinobot" 

She doesn't even act surprised as she never knew about Dinobot. Teltoli gives a tried salute at Iron Raptor and turns away, the after affects of battle just beginning to load on her. Tiredly, she picked up Stinkbomb, and headed off to the CR chambers. She put him in and then closed the door.

Teltoli then leaned against the wall of the CR chamber before stepping inside. She wondered is Liono prime was really the fool and not-so-great leader everyone viewed him as. He wasn't even there to help anyone, or the Ark for that matter. He didn't sound that great.. but she had yet to judge for herself..

The CR chamber beeped and let her drift into a dreamless state..
